ContentDesc_Dun Scaith:
The ancient tome recovered by Captain Radlia of the Talons tells of a floating refuge─an island created by Mhachi sorcerers to provide safe haven from calamitous floodwaters. With the disaster that befell the Void Ark, however, the island's intended residents never arrived. Cait Sith is convinced that Diabolos has instead claimed this refuge as his own, transforming what was to be a bastion of hope into a voidsent nest of shadowy nightmare. And it is into this fiendish lair that you must delve.



The Lady Radlia stands ready to bear you across the skies. Assault the island, reclaim the Nullstone, and cast your demonic foes into oblivion!
Instancecontenttextdata_13201_Text: Systems check complete. Initializing armageddon sequence...
Instancecontenttextdata_13203_Text: Aetheromagnetic induction beacon active. Commencing aether transfer.
Instancecontenttextdata_13216_Text: Reactor capacity exceeded. Gravitational collapse imminent.
Instancecontenttextdata_14108_Text: There it is up ahead─the island from the tome! Let's find somewhere to dock this behemoth!
Instancecontenttextdata_14109_Text: These buildings were meant to house the refugees of Mhach. A promised land, forgotten by time...
Instancecontenttextdata_14110_Text: ...The voidsent have claimed this place, just as I suspected. It is become a nest of shadows and despair.
Instancecontenttextdata_14112_Text: By the twitching of my whiskers, there is fell magick ahead. Only the queen herself could radiate malice of this magnitude!
Instancecontenttextdata_14113_Text: Insolent mortals... One does not come uninvited to the Shadow Queen's castle!
Instancecontenttextdata_14114_Text: Forgive me, my queen... This wretched wraith has failed you...
Instancecontenttextdata_14115_Text: Oh, how I love entertaining unexpected guests! And do I spy some familiar faces in the crowd!?
Instancecontenttextdata_14116_Text: Alas, we come to the end of my show... There shall be...no encore...
Instancecontenttextdata_14117_Text: Welcome, mortals, to my citadel of shadows. Have you come to deepen the gloom with an offering of souls?
Instancecontenttextdata_14118_Text: Such pervasive light... It doth steal into the darkest corners, and chase away my shadows...
Instancecontenttextdata_14119_Text: You expect the creature I was before, enfeebled by confinement? Hah! Face me now in the fullness of my power!
Instancecontenttextdata_14120_Text: Shall I thrust open the gate to the void? The night hounds slaver at the scent of your fear...
Instancecontenttextdata_14121_Text: Another rift... Another chance to test your might?
Instancecontenttextdata_14122_Text: Not even in eternal sleep shall you be free from the terror of my weaving!
Instancecontenttextdata_14123_Text: The energies of the nether will be mine! I will bathe in primordial darkness!
Instancecontenttextdata_14124_Text: Bow before the shrieking majesty of the void!
Instancecontenttextdata_14125_Text: What have you done!? You seek to wrest from me control of the portal?
Instancecontenttextdata_14126_Text: So be it. A contest of strength, then! A contest you have no hope of winning.
Instancecontenttextdata_14127_Text: Impossible! I am a lord of the void, you cannot─ Aaarrrggghhh!
Instancecontenttextdata_14128_Text: <pant> <pant> Mine imprisonment...weakened me more than I imagined...
Instancecontenttextdata_14129_Text: But you have not bested me yet! Witness now my true purpose for seeking the queen's rebirth!
Instancecontenttextdata_14130_Text: Yes. The glory! An infinite well of shadow! You have breached Scathach's unholy vessel, and released her power unto me!
Instancecontenttextdata_14131_Text: From the depths of shadow's well shall rise your ruination!
Instancecontenttextdata_14132_Text: Must I entreat the very specter of death to be rid of you!? I care not! I will wager all for your destruction!
Instancecontenttextdata_14133_Text: What more must I have...? How great the flood of darkness...to drown out your light...
Instancecontenttextdata_14134_Text: Creeping shade and silhouette, gather unto me!
Instancecontenttextdata_14135_Text: To me, my protégé! Smother these intruders with the arts that I have taught thee!
Instancecontenttextdata_14136_Text: And still you refuse to dim and submit... Must I try a different tact?
Instancecontenttextdata_14137_Text: Your fate was sealed the moment you set foot in my domain!
Instancecontenttextdata_14138_Text: From a chrysalis of light shall I birth the deepest shadow...
Instancecontenttextdata_14139_Text: Accept my touch, and bask in tenebrous brilliance!
Instancecontenttextdata_14142_Text: Systems check complete. Initializing armageddon sequence...
Instancecontenttextdata_14143_Text: Aetheromagnetic induction beacon active. Commencing aether transfer.
Instancecontenttextdata_14156_Text: Reactor capacity exceeded. Gravitational collapse imminent.
Instancecontenttextdata_14159_Text: Reaping winds, heed my command! Strip the souls from their worthless shells!
Instancecontenttextdata_14160_Text: I see the blossoms of your fragile lives... I need but reach forth and pluck them from their stems!
Instancecontenttextdata_14161_Text: Come closer, come closer! I promise I will give you a show to die for!
Instancecontenttextdata_14163_Text: This tiresome battle hath dragged on overlong. Enough.
Instancecontenttextdata_14164_Text: What's this? Visitors to our fair abode? Pray allow me to be the first to welcome you!
Instancecontenttextdata_14165_Text: Pay attention, or you'll miss the big reveal!
Instancecontenttextdata_14166_Text: Where is the laughter? The thunderous applause? There is simply no pleasing you!
Instancecontenttextdata_14167_Text: Dance with me! Prance with me! Choose your stage! A fiery demise or a watery grave!
Instancecontenttextdata_14168_Text: Shall we begin? Let dominion of your precious skies be decided here and now!
Instancecontenttextdata_14169_Text: And thus the Shadow Queen doth fall. I commend you on your victory.
Instancecontenttextdata_14170_Text: Yes, such skill and strength are deserving of a more fitting stage. Come, mortals─the true master of shadows awaiteth you...
Instancecontenttextdata_14171_Text: Something comes...but it is no voidsent! Be ready for anything!
Instancecontenttextdata_14172_Text: Shadow itself shall be mine armor! Come! Strike your feeble blows in vain!
Instancecontenttextdata_14173_Text: Such defenses will be difficult to pierce... But mind not his boasts! A persistent assault will prevail!
